
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Hero Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid bg-primary ">
        <img class="img-fluid" src="images/hero.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-start">
                <div class="col-lg-8 text-center text-lg-start" style="background-color: rgb(143, 228, 143);">
                    <h1 class=" text-uppercase mb-lg-4" style="font-size: xx-large; box-shadow: 20px;">Adopt a Horse Today</h1>
                </div>  
        
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Hero End -->

    <!-- About Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row gx-5">
                    <div class="bg-light p-4">
                        <ul class="nav nav-pills justify-content-between mb-3" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
                            <li class="nav-item w-50" role="presentation">
                                <button class="nav-link text-uppercase w-100 active" id="pills-1-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill"
                                    data-bs-target="#pills-1" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-1"
                                    aria-selected="true">Our Mission</button>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item w-50" role="presentation">
                                <button class="nav-link text-uppercase w-100" id="pills-2-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill"
                                    data-bs-target="#pills-2" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-2"
                                    aria-selected="false">Our Vission</button>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="tab-content" id="pills-tabContent">
                            <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-1-tab">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">is to rescue, rehabilitate, and rehome horses with compassion, dignity, and purpose.
                                    We strive to be a beacon of hope for horses that have been forgotten, mistreated, or surrendered—offering each one a second chance at life in a safe, loving environment.
                                    Through responsible adoption, education, and community outreach, we work to create lasting bonds between horses and the people who open their hearts to them.
                                    Every horse we save is a life restored.
                                    Every adoption is a story rewritten.</h5>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-2-tab">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">We envision a world where every horse is valued, protected, and given the opportunity to thrive.
                                    A future where horses are no longer abandoned or abused, but instead find healing, love, and purpose through meaningful human connections.
                                    We aim to become a trusted voice in equine welfare—advocating for ethical treatment, raising awareness, and building a community where horses and humans heal and grow together.
                                     Together, we dream of a future where no horse is left behind.</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- About End -->

    <!-- horse Start -->
    <div class="containeer">
        <h1>Featured Horses</h1>
        <div class="horse-list">
          <% horses.forEach(horse => { %>
            <a href="/horses/<%= horse.id %>" class="horse-card-link">
              <div class="horse-card">
                <img src="<%= horse.image %>" alt="<%= horse.name %>">
                <h2><%= horse.name %></h2>
                <p><strong>Breed:</strong> <%= horse.breed %></p>
                <p><strong>Age:</strong> <%= horse.age %> years</p>
                <p><strong>Height:</strong> <%= horse.height %></p>
              </div>
            </a>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
        <div class="center-button">
          <a href="/horses" class="button" style="background-color: rgb(52, 180, 52);">View All Available </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- horse End -->
       
    
   


    <!-- Testimonial Start -->
    
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="owl-carousel testimonial-carousel bg-white p-5">
                        <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                            <div class="position-relative mb-4">
                                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto" src="images/testimonial-1.jpg" alt="">
                                <div class="position-absolute top-100 start-50 translate-middle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-white" style="width: 45px; height: 45px;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-chat-square-quote text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p>I had never owned a horse before, but the team guided me every step of the way. When I met Bella, I knew instantly she was the one. She came from a tough background, but 
                                now she's thriving, and so am I. Every day, she reminds me how powerful second chances can be.</p>
                           
                            <h5 class="text-uppercase">Emily T., California</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                            <div class="position-relative mb-4">
                                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto" src="images/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="">
                                <div class="position-absolute top-100 start-50 translate-middle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-white" style="width: 45px; height: 45px;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-chat-square-quote text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p>We adopted Ranger for our two kids to learn about responsibility, but he’s become so much more than that. He’s gentle, loyal, and full of personality. We can’t imagine our
                                 lives without him. Thank you for bringing such joy into our home.</p>
                            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto">
                            <h5 class="text-uppercase"> Henderson Family, Texas</h5>
                           
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Testimonial End -->

    

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
